title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1980-12-28
description: Mississippi Half Step-> Franklin's Tower, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Bird Song, Little Red Rooster, Althea, Jack Straw Don't Ease Me In, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Casey Jones

reviews.review_text: My birthday show! At last! Finally I get to hear the show the Dead played on the day I was born! And it feels great as it was a good one, with the band quite on form.
Yes, I was at all these and like the year before, probably the best of the 5 or was that the 27 ?, No that was the next year !
